<p class="intro-text">一份用數據診斷台南的人口報告書。
<br>你，真的了解了嗎？</p>

<div class="report-container">
  <div class="report-top-container">
    <div class="report-left">
      <img src="./dist/img/index/logo-report-company.png">
      <p>病歷號碼: TW-VP001</p>
      <p>2017.5.15</p>
    </div>
    <h1 class="report-title">台南市人口診斷報告書</h1>
    <div class="report-right">
      <p>身份：直轄市</p>
      <p>資料統計至 2016 年 12 月</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="report-line"></div>
  <div class="report-bottom-container">
    <section class="report-section">
      <h2>各區診斷情況</h2>
      <p class="report-section-intro">選擇所在的區域，你看出什麼了嗎？</p>

      <!--
        Desktop 
      -->
      <div class="area-map"></div>

      <!-- 
        MObile 
      -->
      <div class="area-list">
        <select class="ui dropdown">
          <option value="">台南市</option>
          <option value="AL">東區</option>
          <option value="AK">Alaska</option>
          <option value="AZ">Arizona</option>
          <option value="AR">Arkansas</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <!-- Map-modal -->
      <div id="map-modal" class="ui modal">
        <i class="close icon"></i>
        <div class="header">
          Profile Picture
        </div>
        <div class="image content">
          <div class="description">
            <div class="ui header">We've auto-chosen a profile image for you.</div>
            <p>We've grabbed the following image from the <a href="https://www.gravatar.com" target="_blank">gravatar</a> image associated with your registered e-mail address.</p>
            <p>Is it okay to use this photo?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <div class="ui black deny button">
            Nope
          </div>
          <div class="ui positive right labeled icon button">
            Yep, that's me
            <i class="checkmark icon"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ui secondary pointing menu">
        <a class="right item" data-container="population">
          人口總數
        </a>
        <a class="right item" data-container="land">
          土地面積
        </a>
        <a class="right item active" data-container="density">
          人口密度
        </a>
      </div>

      <div id="table-list" class="table-container">
        <div class="container population">
          <div class="table-cell" v-for="(sortedData, index) in descendPopulation">
            <p v-if="index === 0" class="color-gray--dark">
              ${sortedData.area}: &nbsp;${sortedData.population} 人
            </p>
            <p v-else>
              <span v-if="index < 10">&nbsp;</span>${index}. <span class="table-data " :class="(index < 4)? 'size-l highlight ': ' '">${sortedData.area}: &nbsp;${sortedData.population}</span> 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container land">
          <div class="table-cell" v-for="(sortedData, index) in descendLand">
            <p v-if="index === 0" class="color-gray--dark">
              ${sortedData.area}: &nbsp;${sortedData.land.slice(0,-2)} 平方公里
            </p>
            <p v-else>
              <span v-if="index < 10">&nbsp;</span>${index}. <span class="table-data " :class="(index < 4)? 'size-l highlight ': ' '">${sortedData.area}: &nbsp;${sortedData.land.slice(0,-2)}</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container density active">
          <div class="table-cell" v-for="(sortedData, index) in descendDensity">
            <p v-if="index === 0" class="color-gray--dark">
              ${sortedData.area}: &nbsp;${sortedData.density} 人 / 平方公里
            </p>
            <p v-else>
              <span v-if="index < 10">&nbsp;</span>${index}. <span class="table-data " :class="(index < 14)? 'red size-s highlight ': (index === 14)? 'tainan' : ' '">${sortedData.area}: &nbsp;${sortedData.density}</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <section>
  </div>
</div>